          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What's the best SEO tool for a dental practice in 2026?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">It depends on your biggest gap. For content creation (the most common need), theStacc publishes 30 dental blog articles automatically at $99/month. For rank tracking, BrightLocal shows where you rank for "dentist near me" at $39/month. For patient reviews, Birdeye automates generation at $299/month. Most practices need content first.</div>
