        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much should a dentist spend on SEO per month?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">$100–300/month covers essentials for single-location practices. theStacc bundle (~$126/month) handles blog and GBP. Add BrightLocal ($39/month) for tracking, totaling $165/month — 90% cheaper than dental marketing agencies ($2,000–5,000/month) while producing more content.</div>
