        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do dentists really need blog content for SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Patients searching "how much do dental implants cost" or "does teeth whitening hurt" need answers. The practice publishing those answers ranks and gets the patient call. Blog content targets hundreds of dental queries your 5-page website can't rank for. Thirty articles monthly builds a compounding content library over 6–12 months.</div>
